The Trogladite Software Awards 1998

And here I am making a completely unknown event sound like it's something
akin to the Comedy Awards :) Well, we would like your help (well, your
votes) to decide the winners for the following categories. Unfortunately,
you can't vote for whoever you like, you must pick from the nominees.

